---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="HB 6 Impact Survey — Violence-Free Schools Alliance">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pt-12 pb-8">
    <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">VFSA Research Project</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2">Is HB 6 making Texas schools safer?</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-700 max-w-3xl">
      Texas House Bill 6 took effect June 20, 2025. The Violence-Free Schools Alliance
      is gathering ground-truth from Texas educators on how the law is being implemented
      and whether it's reducing violence in classrooms.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700 max-w-3xl">
      Share your experience. It takes <strong>3–5 minutes</strong>, responses are
      <strong>anonymous</strong>, and the results will be used to push for real
      accountability.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <a href="/teacher" class="card hover:shadow-md transition block">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <span
          class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0"
          style="background-color: var(--brand-blue);"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >T</span>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl">I'm a teacher</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
            Tell us what HB 6 looks like from your classroom — awareness, support,
            retaliation concerns, and whether it's actually improving safety.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-block font-semibold" style="color: var(--brand-blue);">
            Start teacher survey →
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/administrator" class="card hover:shadow-md transition block">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <span
          class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0"
          style="background-color: var(--brand-navy);"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >A</span>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl">I'm an administrator</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
            Principals, APs, CBCs, and district leaders: share trends, implementation
            challenges, and what's working (or not) on your campus.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-block font-semibold" style="color: var(--brand-navy);">
            Start administrator survey →
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16">
    <div class="card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-gold);">
      <h3>Your privacy</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
        Responses are collected without any identifying information. IP addresses are
        not logged with responses. If you choose to share your email for the VFSA
        newsletter at the end, it's stored in a separate table that is never linked
        to your survey answers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
